org.svvrl.goal.core.aut.game

Interface SmallProgressMeasureListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.util.EventListener

    public interface SmallProgressMeasureListener
extends java.util.EventListener
    This interface provides listeners which are interesting in the small progress measures of the parity game solver SmallProgressMeasureSolver.

    Ming-Hsien Tsai
